title: Turkmenistan GDP Constant Prices
description: GDP Constant Prices in Turkmenistan decreased to 31.20 USD Billion in 2020 from 44.57 USD Billion in 2019. GDP Constant Prices in Turkmenistan averaged 19.75 USD Billion from 1990 until 2020, reaching an all time high of 44.57 USD Billion in 2019 and a record low of 7.91 USD Billion in 1997. This page provides - Turkmenistan GDP Current Prices - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: SESRIC - The Statistical, Economic & Social Res. & Training Centre for Islamic Countries
